oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Dollywood
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Banjo; Dollywood (Pigeon Forge, Tenn.); Metal photoplates; Musical instruments; Parton, Dolly; Split Fountain Printing; Violin; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (blue, green, and split fountain, red to orange) advertising the amusement park Dollywood. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Dollywood logo and woodcuts of a microphone, banjo, violin (fiddle), and tree.
